Package de.gmxhome.conrad.jpos.jpos_base.linedisplay

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LineDisplayInterface
    Interface for methods that implement property setter and method calls for the LineDisplay device category.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DisplayText
    Output request executor for LineDisplay method DisplayText.
    Factory
    General part of LineDisplay factory for JPOS devices using this framework.
    LineDisplayProperties
    Class containing the display specific properties, their default values and default implementations of LineDisplayInterface.
    LineDisplayService
    LineDisplay service implementation.
    LineDisplayService.ControlChar
    Class describing control characters in display data.
    LineDisplayService.DisplayData
    Class describing displayable part of display data.
    LineDisplayService.DisplayDataPart  
    LineDisplayService.EscBitmap
    Class describing bitmap escape sequences ESC|#B.
    LineDisplayService.EscNormalize
    Class describing normalize escape sequences ESC|N.
    LineDisplayService.EscSimple
    Class describing simple attribute setting escape sequences ESC|[!]xC, where x is one of b, i, rv, tb or tp.
    LineDisplayService.EscUnknown
    Class describing unknown escape sequence.
